&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;As a Concierge Receptionist at Sollis Health, you will be the first point of contact for our members and patients in their time of need, creating a welcoming and personable first impression as you assist them in scheduling their medical appointments. You will be responsible for managing our phone lines and addressing member concerns in real time, demonstrating agility while ensuring a welcoming environment for our high-caliber clientele.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
