&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In the role of an Advanced Care Provider (Nurse Practitioner) you will provide concierge emergency medical care to Sollis Health patients in our clinics with the supervision/oversight of an attending Physician. This is a pivotal role as part of a growing organization providing seamless care to both adult and pediatric patients for cases that would usually be treated in a traditional emergency room.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Beverly Hills Part Time-10a-6p - 16 hours/week. Rotating holidays and weekends.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
